                <h1>Leaonna Odom&#039;s career day leads Duke women&#039;s basketball to first-round victory vs. Belmont</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/4896efe6-461e-4ea7-ad59-90df647f0667.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Leaonna&#x20;Odom&#x20;had&#x20;a&#x20;career&#x20;day&#x20;to&#x20;lead&#x20;the&#x20;Blue&#x20;Devils&#x20;in&#x20;scoring&#x20;against&#x20;Belmont." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Leaonna Odom had a career day to lead the Blue Devils in scoring against Belmont.

