                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>And if Odom plays the way she did against Belmont, the Blue Devils could very likely soon be on their way to Albany, N.Y., for a potential date with the ever-dominant Huskies next weekend.</p>
<p>“I think wanting to advance and give our seniors another game,” Odom said. “That makes me want to take the pressure off of them, so I have to do what I need to do in order for us to advance.”</p>
